        "body": "I understand your concern regarding the contrast and difficulty distinguishing colours in the current Alucard variation. ðŸ˜¥\r\n\r\nIt is challenging to achieve the right balance between adequate contrast and compliance with the WCAG standard, especially for light themes.\r\n\r\nWhile designing Alucard, we recognized that this could lead to less noticeable contrast for some elements than dark variants. However, we will continue to iterate on the palette of all variants to improve this. ðŸ§©",
